                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="text-wrap">
                
                <p><b>PCI DSS - The Payment Card Industry Data Security Standard (PCI DSS)</b></p>
<p>PCIDSS has served as the de facto standard for protecting cardholder data across the world since its implementation in 2004.</p>
<p>The standards were developed by the PCI Security Standards Council (PCI SSC), a global forum that brings together payment industry stakeholders to develop and drive the adoption of data security standards and resources for safe payments worldwide.</p>
<p><a href="https://www.bitdefender.com/blog/businessinsights/the-four-industries-that-need-to-prioritize-cybersecurity-the-most/">Discover more</a></p>
<p><a href="/en-us/business/products/inquire/">Ger compliant</a></p>


                
              </div>
            </div>
          
        </div>
      
