</div>

    


          </div>
          <div class="content we-row we-align-items-center">
            <div class="we-container">
              <div class="inner dex">
                
                <q class="h3"><p>“Bitdefender MDR assures me that someone is watching our entire network in realtime, including when my staff and I are not in the office. As we’ve shifted to teleworking with COVID-19, we’re able to protect our information assets regardless of where employees are logging in from. MDR is an extension of my team to support the mission of the Archdiocese.”  </p>
</q>
                <p>IT Director for an Archdiocese</p>
                

